## Backend – filer och blueprints

| Fil | Prefix | Roll |
|-----|--------|------|
| `app.py` | – | Skapar Flask-app, `db`, `ProxyFix` vid `DATABASE_URL`, session cookies, **LANDING_HOSTS**, statiska routes |
| `backend/auth.py` | – | `get_current_user()`, `login_required` |
| `backend/models.py` | – | `User`, `Team`, `TeamPlayer`, `Match`, `MatchPlayer` |
| `backend/mail.py` | – | `send_mail()` (SMTP via `MAIL_*`) |
| `backend/schema_migrations.py` | – | `ensure_user_email_and_reset_columns(db)` |
| `backend/routes/auth_routes.py` | `/api/auth` | register, login, logout, me, profile, forgot/reset password |
| `backend/routes/teams_routes.py` | `/api/teams` | CRUD lag (per inloggad användare) |
| `backend/routes/matches_routes.py` | `/api/matches` | lista, spara, hämta, radera, rensa allt |
| `backend/routes/public_routes.py` | `/api/public` | `GET /matches` – publik läslista (CORS `*`, max 500) |

